Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.55,0:00:01.95,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Please—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.95,0:00:04.48,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Marry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.55,0:00:08.37,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, I guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.37,0:00:11.90,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,If you insist so much, I'll marry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.08,0:00:20.76,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Look, look, Ryu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.76,0:00:24.62,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga-chan had this many babies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.03,0:00:29.29,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,They're your kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:36.27,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,It was a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.52,0:00:43.52,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,This is what happens when I rent crappy DVDs over my summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.26,0:00:49.49,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a dream, but that would be the worst future ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.61,0:00:52.05,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.05,0:00:53.87,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I had an unpleasant dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.87,0:00:54.70,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:00:57.93,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You were a dog, and the dog was my husband…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.93,0:01:01.08,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it was the worst dream ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.61,0:02:43.91,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,A warning dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.91,0:02:50.94,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the worst possible future is waiting for us unless we take countermeasures against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:52.48,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It's a warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:03:00.07,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,So, one of us should give our full support to the other starting tomorrow during the trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.69,0:03:04.20,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,I get that, but... why badminton?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:05.37,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.83,0:03:10.54,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to decide on the supporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:14.00,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever use fire, understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:16.71,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget to mix the pickle paste. {Nukazuke is paste used to make pickles. It's made from part of the rice}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:19.20,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget to change Inko-chan's water every day and night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.20,0:03:20.76,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Read my note for the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.97,0:03:23.32,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:27.47,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Go... where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.80,0:03:30.23,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,I told you before, the trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.99,0:03:32.48,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,See ya, Ya-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:39.15,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the weather will be pretty nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.20,0:03:42.54,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you for that so-called plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.36,0:03:47.46,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.46,0:03:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are you really sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:53.04,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I'll let you be winner so just get this off of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.98,0:03:59.35,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,If it wasn't for that stupid dog's intervention, I would have won.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.35,0:04:03.77,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,You were punished for trying to compete with me in your strongest sport.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.77,0:04:06.60,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, nothing good happens when dogs are involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:10.72,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,But, is this really going to work out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:12.06,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.82,0:04:16.31,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,By the time this trip is over you and Minorin will be—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.91,0:04:19.02,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.02,0:04:21.47,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.47,0:04:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two are right on time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:25.67,Default,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, that's admirable!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:29.25,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, where's your energy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.25,0:04:30.29,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, raise your voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:31.83,Announce,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:33.11,Announce,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What the—?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.86,0:04:32.14,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.74,0:04:35.02,Default,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, the weather is perfect, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.02,0:04:36.09,Announce,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.09,0:04:36.42,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.74,0:04:38.97,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Amin isn't here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.97,0:04:40.88,Default,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,We still have a bit until our meeting time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:42.67,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.37,0:04:47.62,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, what's with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:49.76,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:51.18,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:53.74,Default,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,You're two minutes late, Ami!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.74,0:04:55.57,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Amin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:04:57.71,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, you stupid chihuahua!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.43,0:05:03.01,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where everyone is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:05.01,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Stop running you stupid chihuahua!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.01,0:05:06.74,Default,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,We're right here Ami!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.38,0:05:16.73,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this is really delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.73,0:05:18.59,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,It has a plum in it, and it's really tasty! {Note that ume means plum and umee mean's yummy/tastes good so she's doing a little pun.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.59,0:05:19.98,Default,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,That's Takasu for ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:21.33,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to be my bride?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.33,0:05:21.96,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:24.63,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Aww, you're so mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:27.33,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, now that I think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.33,0:05:30.08,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka-san doesn't seem to be here, is she late?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:31.43,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, you should conta—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.49,0:05:35.98,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:38.68,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you were awake stupid chihuahua?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.68,0:05:40.82,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were sleeping with your eyes open.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:41.06,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.58,0:05:44.05,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to fight on a trip, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.58,0:05:47.70,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, what were you doing over summer break, Kawashima?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:49.02,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was stuck working the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:52.41,Default,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,So, you started working again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.02,0:05:54.02,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What about you Minorin?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:56.16,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,After school club, part-time job...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.16,0:05:57.08,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,...after school club, part-time job...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.08,0:05:58.69,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,...after school club, after school club, part-time job...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:05:59.64,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,...after school club, part-time job...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.64,0:06:01.20,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,...after school club, part-time job, after school club—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.97,0:06:01.00,Default 2,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,What about you Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.97,0:06:05.46,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, what is it Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.56,0:06:02.97,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I was making...{timing a bit weird here}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.15,0:06:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.34,0:06:16.30,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,I just heard a weird voice say, "senpai," what is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:20.48,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It's a collection of songs that have mysterious ghost voices in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:22.06,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.06,0:06:25.08,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,No, it called for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.76,0:06:28.06,Default,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka, you like horror related things?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.06,0:06:29.36,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, I might.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:32.57,Default,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,That's unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.57,0:06:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although, it's also unexpected that Kushieda can't stand scary stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:38.25,Default 2,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah, I totally can't stand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:40.08,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand it sooo much that I—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.43,0:06:45.59,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin really can't stand occult, horror, and ghost related things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:51.31,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,That's why the two of us will scare Minorin to bits!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.31,0:06:56.12,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Once she's fallen into the depths of fear, you'll save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.12,0:06:58.35,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,"I'll protect Kushieda!" That's what you'll say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.75,0:07:02.61,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,The "Scare Minorin and Have a Knight Save Her" plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.61,0:07:06.47,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I absolutely forbid scary stories!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.47,0:07:08.19,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.00,0:07:12.28,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,The sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:33.22,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... how far are you going to make us walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:35.14,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you see it yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:36.93,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Head around behind here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:39.86,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,You should be able to get straight onto the deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.37,0:07:44.07,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,This is Amin's villa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.07,0:07:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We get to stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.58,0:07:47.02,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,That's right Minori-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:48.86,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,That's awesome, it's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.27,0:07:52.60,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Although, we have to clean up first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.60,0:07:54.36,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,No one has been here since last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.36,0:07:55.97,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,S-Since last year?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.97,0:07:57.53,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:08:00.78,Default Italic,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,This... will be a gruesome battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.78,0:08:01.74,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.74,0:08:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this beautiful beach is right in front of our eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.36,0:08:06.41,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,We can clean later, later!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.41,0:08:08.45,Default,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,That's true, we can clean afterwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.45,0:08:10.20,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.08,0:08:13.34,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going, too, What about you Takasu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:30.86,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I cleaning… alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.29,0:08:36.10,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,It feels sooo good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.10,0:08:36.70,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.08,0:08:38.25,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.25,0:08:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:42.04,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that kind of look like someone's head?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.70,0:08:45.03,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,It's a beached corpse!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:49.25,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?! I let myself touch its juices!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.79,0:08:52.21,Default,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they're having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.16,0:08:55.65,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,So you really came, Yuusaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:57.47,Default,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:09:02.16,Default,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,If Takasu's going, there's no way that I, his best friend, wouldn't come along.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.51,0:09:05.04,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,What about the student council?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.72,0:09:07.93,Default,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.58,0:09:10.39,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.14,0:09:12.99,Default,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.48,0:09:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ami said to go buy the groceries.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:17.46,Default,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently there's a bike in the storeroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.46,0:09:18.51,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,A bike?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.51,0:09:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, take Taiga in that case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.02,0:09:22.95,Default,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka's going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.78,0:09:27.02,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.02,0:09:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bikes are scary, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.09,0:09:28.67,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:32.53,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Drive carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.53,0:09:33.71,Default,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.06,0:09:36.06,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.04,0:09:38.40,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Aww man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.40,0:09:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You blew the chance to be alone together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:43.73,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I have a reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.15,0:09:49.71,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,We have to find a place to use for our plan before those two get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.71,0:09:51.36,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you be honest and just say you were shy—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.80,0:09:54.32,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,There was a mosquito, a mosquito.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.08,0:09:56.86,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:09:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A good place we can use...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.98,0:10:04.04,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,This is... the wash room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:06.62,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,I need to clean this place, too—huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:07.77,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:08.74,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.74,0:10:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just didn't notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:10.52,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.52,0:10:12.17,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll get out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:13.52,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.93,0:10:15.40,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty daring...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.77,0:10:18.54,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Barging in when a girl's showering.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:21.18,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,I-It wasn't on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:24.16,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, we don't have to tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:25.72,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:27.58,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, don't you want to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.58,0:10:29.09,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—do what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.93,0:10:31.12,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Clean the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.58,0:10:35.02,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, what on earth were you expecting?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.98,0:10:38.07,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that face? It's hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.65,0:10:42.91,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga~!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:44.03,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stupid chi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:47.48,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Made it look like she was showering...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:50.30,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,and fiddled with your pure heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.95,0:10:53.34,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,So, are you done investigating the second floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.32,0:10:55.75,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why you get manipulated so easily by that stupid chi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.97,0:11:00.63,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I'll have a look myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.23,0:11:03.97,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,While I'm at it, I'll go complain to that stupid chi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:07.39,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stupid chi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.87,0:11:19.43,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,That stupid chi was really showering this time…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.03,0:11:24.45,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,She was just like, bam... bam...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:26.79,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,and BAM—!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:28.83,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,That's unnecessary!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.64,0:11:32.78,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.82,0:11:35.29,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,You sure bought a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:35.84,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Kitamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:37.24,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,He said he was going to park the bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.24,0:11:38.51,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:40.17,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:40.97,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:43.89,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,You did the shopping for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:44.51,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.19,0:11:48.86,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.86,0:11:52.14,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, something just... something was on my neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:53.47,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,It's just your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:55.86,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has to be, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.70,0:11:59.98,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,No, I definitely felt something there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.98,0:12:02.57,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,It was slimy or rather seaweed-ish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.57,0:12:05.78,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,It does smell like seaweed! It is seaweed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:08.24,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a creature's ghost that was entangled by seaweed—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.24,0:12:10.05,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Entanglement by seaweed means it's an otter's corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.05,0:12:12.03,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,An otter full of seaweed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.03,0:12:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the curse of the otter and seaweed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.37,0:12:16.04,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want the spicy flavor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:20.21,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I want the spicy one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.21,0:12:22.95,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I can't eat it unless it's sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.32,0:12:24.20,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ryuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:28.43,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I'll make a sweet one for you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.39,0:12:32.37,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Are you giving special treatment to Aisaka-san again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.37,0:12:35.17,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Girls won't like you if you do stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.17,0:12:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say for instance... Minori-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:39.11,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Did you call me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.18,0:12:42.30,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.30,0:12:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're well prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.62,0:12:45.21,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.21,0:12:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is to put the sauce in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.13,0:12:49.41,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys should get ready to eat, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.41,0:12:51.16,Default,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is it time to prepare for dinner already?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.78,0:12:53.45,Default,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help set up the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:55.73,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.66,0:12:59.20,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Taiga?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.20,0:13:01.22,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Yuusaku, are you insane?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.24,0:13:05.15,Default,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry, I just heard Takasu's voice and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.15,0:13:06.26,Default,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot that there were girls here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.87,0:13:08.43,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,What are you stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:10.01,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga, get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:11.01,Default,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.08,0:13:16.24,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,You god-sent child of narcissism!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.24,0:13:17.31,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Give me your nudies!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.31,0:13:19.21,Default,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Oh come on, cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.21,0:13:20.75,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,You can't say that when you look like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.75,0:13:22.05,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Stop pretending to be innocent! {A Kamatoto is a girl that acts pretends to be innocent}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.77,0:13:23.00,Default 2,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.49,0:13:23.61,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,That's good, that's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.65,0:13:31.56,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,I think... I just saw something... black and fluffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.56,0:13:33.81,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,I-It was probably the seaweed ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:35.98,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Sea—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:36.29,Default,Mionri,0000,0000,0000,,weed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.23,0:13:38.29,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:40.77,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Yuusaku, you are the worst...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.77,0:13:41.25,Default,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.70,0:13:43.16,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Just get out of here you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.16,0:13:44.13,Default,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.44,0:13:51.79,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Beware everyone, there's an evil spirit in this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.79,0:13:54.00,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something I can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.69,0:13:58.04,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Make the curry as spicy as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:13:59.56,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.32,0:14:03.95,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it looks good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.95,0:14:08.32,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,I just made it with what was at hand, but I made it as spicy as I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:09.54,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.54,0:14:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:12.03,Default,Everyone,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.90,0:14:15.62,Default,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, this works.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.18,0:14:17.08,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it tastes good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.13,0:14:20.55,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... it's not as spicy as I thought it'd be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.87,0:14:21.38,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.04,0:14:22.68,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.68,0:14:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want some, too, Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.66,0:14:28.17,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, it's not that—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.03,0:14:30.13,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.78,0:14:36.03,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It's freakin' spicy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.03,0:14:36.87,Default,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,My throat is—!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:39.02,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot—No, it hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.29,0:14:42.27,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes! Wam-bam thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.66,0:14:44.45,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Here it comes again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.45,0:14:46.38,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you guys okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.38,0:14:47.15,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.94,0:14:49.42,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,You're freakin' awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.42,0:14:51.84,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,It's insanely spicy and insanely delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.75,0:14:56.40,Default,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, it mysteriously lures me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.40,0:14:58.62,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I feel kind of strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:00.87,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there are seconds, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.14,0:15:02.30,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:07.47,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I thought I was gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.79,0:15:11.51,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I'll wash the dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:13.18,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.88,0:15:14.77,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.77,0:15:17.04,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's because I had something spicy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.04,0:15:18.39,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I want some medicine for my stomach ache.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.39,0:15:19.38,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,A stomach ache?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.38,0:15:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the medicine is—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.25,0:15:22.15,Default,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka, you're not feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.56,0:15:24.35,Default,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,I brought some stomach ache medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.35,0:15:25.32,Default,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,You want to come along?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:28.15,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,W-What, t-that's—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.72,0:15:29.72,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:30.61,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—Hold on—!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.48,0:15:33.46,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,It's a chance to be alone together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.06,0:15:34.81,Default,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.81,0:15:35.97,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing really.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.46,0:15:37.57,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll leave it to ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.57,0:15:38.20,Default,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:43.83,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey-hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.22,0:15:47.97,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,My stomach hurts, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.97,0:15:48.55,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:49.59,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.62,0:15:51.59,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:52.69,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.27,0:15:55.04,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,You were just spaced out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.31,0:15:59.45,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't get bored looking at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:00.85,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Was that a compliment?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:02.31,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:03.41,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.80,0:16:07.96,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, would you like to go out to the bea—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.59,0:16:08.96,Default 2,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takasu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.96,0:16:10.31,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Can you get the cup over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.31,0:16:12.01,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.36,0:16:13.32,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, what were you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.22,0:16:16.29,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.07,0:16:25.21,Default,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Was that enough water?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.24,0:16:28.99,Default,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.99,0:16:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it seem like it's working?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:31.77,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.77,0:16:33.63,Default,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.63,0:16:36.68,Default,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,When I see you in pain, I feel painful, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:40.33,Default,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, you want to lie down since you're in pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.58,0:16:47.53,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, your washing techniques are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.53,0:16:50.46,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I do it a lot at my part-time job, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.93,0:16:53.88,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Your curry was amazing as well, Takasu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.88,0:16:54.83,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.83,0:16:56.00,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.00,0:16:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you something nice for helping me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.34,0:17:01.24,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell anyone, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.55,0:17:07.20,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, does the maccha taste good? {It's green tea flavor}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.20,0:17:09.27,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Uh—Yeah, it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.27,0:17:10.83,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,The red beans are iffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.06,0:17:16.71,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't the stars amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.71,0:17:18.51,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,T-They're beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:21.06,Default Italic,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,It's just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.94,0:17:23.64,Default Italic,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Is it my chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.62,0:17:29.43,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kushieda, do you h-have a b-boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.75,0:17:37.20,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think that seaweed ghost is still around?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:37.68,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.68,0:17:41.95,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, have you ever seen a ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.52,0:17:43.44,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.44,0:17:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.43,0:17:48.36,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that ghosts are real.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.36,0:17:54.54,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,But I've never seen one and I don't believe those that say they have.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.54,0:17:55.19,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.19,0:17:58.09,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,And there's another thing that I think about similarly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:18:03.56,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that one day I'll fall in love, marry, and live happily.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:07.56,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,But I've never had that feeling with someone before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.79,0:18:14.02,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,The people out there who fall in love like it's so normal... seem so far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.02,0:18:16.93,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Because I can't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.44,0:18:19.68,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't ghosts after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never see any for the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:22.63,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,I've kind of almost given up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:27.49,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,So the answer to your question is that I don't have a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.35,0:18:29.49,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Takasu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.49,0:18:31.74,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see ghosts?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:33.47,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.47,0:18:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might just want to see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.27,0:18:40.71,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I go to haunted places and watch scary DVDs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.71,0:18:41.93,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,I also think...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.16,0:18:47.35,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,People with the sixth sense were probably surprised the first time they saw a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:51.77,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Some people probably see them, but pretend they don't,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.77,0:18:57.57,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,and some may have worked so hard and were finally able to see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.38,0:19:03.34,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you shouldn't decide that you'll never see any for the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.31,0:19:05.65,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.65,0:19:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A UFO?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.59,0:19:09.73,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, that's a satellite.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.73,0:19:12.09,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,A satellite?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.09,0:19:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aww, I thought it was a UFO.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:24.17,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you get to see a ghost one day, Kushieda.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.87,0:19:29.17,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,I-I think there's a ghost out there that wants to be seen by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.00,0:19:34.98,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's why weird stuff keeps happening today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.03,0:19:38.94,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,The seaweed ghost—it's trying to attract my attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.98,0:19:42.42,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:45.63,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'll see one someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.63,0:19:46.28,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:47.70,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.14,0:19:51.33,Default Italic,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,You're a strange one...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.81,0:19:58.75,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Ryuuji, It seems like my stomach's feeling better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.75,0:20:00.04,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay... and?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.37,0:20:08.81,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Phew, I ate a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.18,0:20:10.62,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,And for some reason I did, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.34,0:20:14.83,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what should we do tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.30,0:20:16.31,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.67,0:20:19.23,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:21.53,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It's not going well for you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.99,0:20:23.48,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,And what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.48,0:20:26.74,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm supposed to be the supporter this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:29.48,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, but I sure am tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:36.87,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering how blissful it would be to be with Kitamura-kun all day long, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.87,0:20:40.21,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I'd probably die young of nervousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.21,0:20:41.76,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.36,0:20:45.01,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm totally fine when I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.01,0:20:47.01,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean? That's rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.45,0:20:52.05,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It's so stupid. Even though we're in this huge room, we closely sit together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.84,0:20:55.77,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I guess my body's used to that cramped apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.77,0:20:56.65,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.03,0:21:01.01,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji, I thought about it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.01,0:21:04.14,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,That dream... it might be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:06.17,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.33,0:21:09.32,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.98,0:21:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.98,0:21:11.66,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.66,0:21:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.75,0:21:17.41,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,What the—?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.41,0:21:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I leave my bag in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.02,0:21:24.30,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.16,0:21:26.91,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,And it's kind of slimy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.60,0:21:30.70,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji! What'd you do make to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.70,0:21:34.39,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It was in my bag, but, it was warm when I touched it just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.02,0:21:37.58,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It's as if someone's just been wearing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.58,0:21:40.30,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,M-My room's strange, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.30,0:21:42.25,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,There's long hair on my pillow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.37,0:21:45.02,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,W-What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.02,0:21:46.86,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,I-It must be—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.92,0:21:53.41,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,T-This has to be a dream, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.41,0:21:55.08,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, it's a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.39,0:21:58.99,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,It's the continuation of that dream where we're dogs living in a dog house.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.99,0:22:01.73,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, we'll wake up eventually, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.73,0:22:03.13,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,We will, we will!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.92,0:22:04.96,Default Italic,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.80,0:23:37.11,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Scary, scary, scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.11,0:23:38.59,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Horror's scary! Ghosts are scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.59,0:23:40.01,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Demon beasts are scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.01,0:23:41.08,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down Kushieda!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.08,0:23:43.85,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,But... the scariest thing might be a UFO.
